name: Mizuchi
skill: Deals (264/384) DMG to the enemy with the most HP. Target deals (27%/39%) less DMG for a limited time.

additional_data.description: This young whippersnapper dreams of growing up to be like his old man, the rain dragon Yinlong. He's true to his heritage and got the attitude down pat--unfortunately, his young age means he's naive to a fault, and is all too easily trickable as a result.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ At the beginning of the game, he was named "Aqua Draggy"

main: "My dad's Yinglong! I bet he's way awesomer than your dad!"
skill: "I'll show you how scary dragons can be!"
summon: "I wanna come with you! Pretty please?"
limit_break: "One day I'll be as cool as my dad! You'll see!"
